examples.en: The government decreed a national holiday.
The change was decreed by the President.
Fate decreed that we would win the lottery.
The government decreed that a new tax be / should be imposed.
The City Council has decreed that all dogs must be kept on a leash.
When Adonis died Zeus decreed that he should spend winters in the underworld with Persephone and spend summers with Aphrodite.
